---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="Grenoble Airport (GNB) Taxi Alternative | Private VTC | ShipCars"
    description="Need a taxi alternative at Grenoble Airport (GNB)? Book your private VTC with a driver. Fixed price, comfort, premium service for your transfers to Grenoble and ski resorts.">

    <section class="page-hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1><strong>Taxi Alternative</strong> at Grenoble Airport (GNB)</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Your <strong>private VTC driver</strong> service for direct, comfortable, and fixed-price transfers.</p>
            <a href="/#booking" class="cta-button">Book my VTC from GNB</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
        <div class="container text-container">
            <h2>A Personalized Welcome upon your Arrival in Grenoble</h2>
            <p>
                Grenoble Alpes Is√®re Airport (GNB) is the ideal gateway to the Oisans and Vercors resorts. To start your stay without delay, our <strong>VTC service at Grenoble Airport</strong> offers you immediate pick-up. No more uncertain waiting: your <strong>private driver</strong> will be waiting for you upon your arrival to take you directly to your destination.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features-section bg-light">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">The Advantages of a <strong>Private Driver</strong> over a Taxi at GNB</h2>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="icon">‚è∞</div>
                    <h3><strong>Punctuality</strong> and Flight Tracking</h3>
                    <p>
                        We track your flight in real time. In case of a delay, we adjust our arrival time <strong>at no extra cost</strong>. Your transfer is guaranteed, regardless of any unforeseen events.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="icon">üéø</div>
                    <h3><strong>Ski Resort</strong> Specialist</h3>
                    <p>
                        From GNB, we provide direct connections to major resorts like <strong>Alpe d'Huez</strong> and <strong>Les Deux Alpes</strong>. Our <a href="/vehicle"><strong>spacious vehicle</strong></a> is perfect for your ski equipment.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="icon">‚úÖ</div>
                    <h3>A <strong>Price Known in Advance</strong></h3>
                    <p>
                        The price of your trip is fixed at the time of booking. Enjoy a stress-free transfer without worrying about the final cost, a <strong>transparent alternative to a taxi</strong> at Grenoble Airport.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Your <strong>VTC at Grenoble Airport</strong> is waiting for you</h2>
            <a href="/#booking" class="cta-button">Book my transfer</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    :root { 
        --accent: #35c2b5; 
        --dark-bg: #2d3a4c;
        --light-bg: #f8f9fa;
        --text-color: #333;
    }
    .page-hero {
        background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.5), rgba(0,0,0,0.5)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1599827551004-9359f53856d1?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop') no-repeat center center;
        background-size: cover;
        color: white;
        padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .page-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2em, 5vw, 3.5em); text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.7); }
    .page-hero .subtitle { font-size: 1.2em; opacity: 0.9; max-width: 700px; margin: 1rem auto 2rem auto; }
    
    .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
        background-color: var(--accent); 
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 50px; 
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .cta-button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    .content-section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    .text-container { max-width: 800px; text-align: center; margin: 0 auto; }
    .text-container h2 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .text-container p { font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.7; color: #555; }

    .features-section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    .features-section h2 { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; }
    .feature-card {
        background: white;
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        text-align: center;
    }
    .feature-card .icon { font-size: 2.5em; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .feature-card h3 { margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--dark-bg); }
    .feature-card p { color: #666; line-height: 1.6; }
    .feature-card a { font-weight: bold; }

    .links-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    @media (min-width: 768px) { .links-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
    .link-card {
        border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }
    .link-card h4 { font-size: 1.4em; }

    .cta-section {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg);
        color: white;
        padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .cta-section p { max-width: 600px; margin: 1rem auto 2rem auto; opacity: 0.9; }

    .bg-light { background-color: var(--light-bg); }
    .bg-light .text-container p, .bg-light .feature-card p { color: #333; }
</style>